data.description: JUST REDUCED! Seller offering $10k towards buyers closing costs!! Welcome to this remarkable property featuring a spacious 3-car garage in the Verrado Community! Owned solar- low electric bills! Prepare to be impressed by a harmonious open layout showcasing soothing palette, tile flooring, dazzling light fixtures, & multi-sliders merging the indoor w/the outdoor. The beautiful chef's kitchen displays white cabinetry adorned w/crown moulding, quartz counters, stylish mosaic backsplash, SS appliances, wall oven, a walk-in pantry, & an island equipped w/a breakfast bar. Discover a versatile loft ideal for an additional living space! Main retreat offers soft carpet in all the right places, a private bathroom w/dual sinks, & a walk-in closet. Charming backyard w/a covered patio & turf.
